                <h1>Critical Police Background Check Disqualifiers</h1>
                <p>Police background checks can reveal disqualifiers that may impact employment opportunities. Major disqualifiers include felony convictions, recent criminal activity, substance abuse, dishonesty in applications, or negative driving records. Knowing these factors is crucial for applicants wanting to work in sensitive fields like law enforcement or education.</p>
